## Lab-Grown 2ct Round Diamond Prices

Lab-grown 2ct round diamonds from Blue Nile represent the most dramatic price arbitrage in the 2ct market. D-VVS1 IGI-certified lab-grown stones start at $2,810 — against $33,390 for the natural equivalent. That is an 87% discount for a stone that is chemically, optically, and physically identical to natural diamond.

| Stone | Cert | Color/Clarity | Price |
|-------|------|---------------|-------|
| [IGI 2ct D-VVS1 Ideal Lab-Grown](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/28629934) | IGI | D-VVS1 | $2,810 |
| [IGI 2ct D-VVS1 Ideal Lab-Grown](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/28953470) | IGI | D-VVS1 | $2,810 |
| [IGI 2ct D-FL Ideal Lab-Grown](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/29372746) | IGI | D-FL | $5,190 |
| [GCAL 2ct D-IF Ideal Lab-Grown](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/28638054) | GCAL | D-IF | $5,780 |
| [IGI 2ct D-FL Ideal Lab-Grown](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/29314466) | IGI | D-FL | $6,690 |
| [GCAL 2ct E-VVS1 Ideal Lab-Grown](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/29091853) | GCAL | E-VVS1 | $13,730 |
| [GCAL 2ct D-VVS1 Ideal Lab-Grown](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/29027726) | GCAL | D-VVS1 | $14,020 |

The IGI D-VVS1 at $2,810 and the GCAL D-VVS1 at $14,020 are both D-VVS1. The $11,000 gap between them is the certification premium — GCAL is a stricter grader than IGI and commands a higher price. The GCAL D-VVS1 is closer in grading rigor to a GIA-equivalent stone.

The critical trade-off for lab-grown at 2ct: **resale value.** A natural 2ct G-VS1 at $22,460 will resell for $9,000–$11,000 (40–50% of retail). The lab-grown D-VVS1 at $2,810 will resell for $280–$560 (10–20% of retail). If resale matters to you, natural is the only answer at any carat weight. The [lab grown round diamond guide](/lab-grown-round-diamond) covers this in detail.

![2ct lab-grown vs natural round diamond — price comparison D-VVS1 quality, IGI vs GIA certification](/images/2ct-lab-grown-vs-natural-round-diamond-price.avif "2ct Lab-Grown vs Natural Round Diamond Price Comparison")

